                <li>"Walk" up to a high plank by placing one hand, then the other, where your elbows were.</li>
                <li>Perform one "pop-up" by jumping your feet out wide and back in.</li>
                <li>Walk back down to the forearm plank. That's one rep.</li>
              </ol>
