                <li>Step one foot back into a deep reverse lunge, both knees at 90 degrees.</li>
                <li>Push off the back foot and drive that same knee up toward your chest in one fluid motion.</li>
                <li>Balance for a second at the top before stepping back into the next lunge.</li>
                <li>Complete all reps on one side before switching.</li>
              </ol>
